<dl id="n12003g"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12003g">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12003g"> 3(g)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Sujet unique</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Seulement la &ldquo;r&egrave;gle du <mark>sujet unique</mark>&rdquo; telle que Th&eacute;odore l&apos;a exprim&eacute;e, est presque un crit&egrave;re du bon langage. <br><font color="green">[Only the &ldquo;rule of the single subject,&rdquo; as it is expressed by Th&eacute;odore, is almost a criterion for good language.]</font> <small> Jacques Boulenger &amp; Andr&eacute; Th&eacute;rive, <a name="SOIR" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#SOIR"><cite title="source">Les Soir&eacute;es du Grammaire-Club</cite></a> (1924) 247</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
